                <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/> <lb n="1"/>Anatole pa<supplied reason="lost">rentes</supplied> <lb n="2"/>fecerunt vixit a<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>nis</ex></expan> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <expan><abbr>mens</abbr><ex>ibus</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="3"/>VIII <expan><abbr>dieb</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> X sibi suis p<supplied reason="lost">osterisque</supplied> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> in <expan><abbr>fr</abbr><ex>onte</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>edes</ex></expan> V in a<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>g</abbr><ex>ro</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>edes</ex></expan> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></supplied>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Das Stück ist heute in einer Villa bei Ansedonia vermauert und befand sich früher im Besitz derselben Familie in der Nähe von Rimini; der Fundort ist unbekannt.</p>
